item.dc:creator: @SandScape SandScape
item.description:
@SandScape wrote:

[quote=“coco zezima, post:2, topic:260264”]Go to your client.java located in your source folder.
From there push ctrl + f if you didnt already know that.
And seach for the coordinates for the teleport you want to change.
For example i wanted to change varrock teleport to Lumbridge.
(These are not atual varrock coordinates) Say they were 2343 4776
So you would go to your client.java and search for that using Ctrl + f. Then change
them to what you want them.[/quote]fail thats going to change the tele commands
